FastAPI requires Python 3.7 or later. So make sure you have a recent version of Python installed. In the project directory, create and activate a dedicated virtual environment for the project:

# below commands setup virtual environment for python3
$ python3 -m venv v1
$ source v1/bin/activate
 you can start intalling packages  using pip install 

 # below commands for windows 
python3 -m venv v1
v1\Scripts\activate

after this start installing packages using pip install 